A self-driving car made by company [`G`] is programed to always keep its distance from the front of a non-self driving (NSD) by [`15`] [`m`]. Another self-driving car made by company [`T`] is programed to always keep its distance from the rear of an NSD by [`20`] [`m`]. 
Consider a case where the relative velocity between [`G`] and [`T`] is [`[$VTG]`] [`m/s`] and [`a = 9`] [`m`] and [`b = 12`] [`m`]. Determine the velocity of the NSD.

